!Mouse Events
OnDesktop Mouse1 :HideMenus
OnDesktop Mouse2 :WorkspaceMenu
OnDesktop Mouse3 :RootMenu
OnDesktop Mouse4 :NextWorkspace
OnDesktop Mouse5 :PrevWorkspace

!Workspaces
Mod4 1 :SendToWorkspace 1
Mod4 2 :SendToWorkspace 2
Mod4 3 :SendToWorkspace 3
Mod4 4 :SendToWorkspace 4

Mod1 1 :Workspace 1
Mod1 2 :Workspace 2
Mod1 3 :Workspace 3
Mod1 4 :Workspace 4

!Windows Functionality
Mod1 Tab :NextWindow
Mod1 Shift Tab :PrevWindow
Mod4 L :NextTab
Mod4 H :PrevTab
Mod1 F4 :Close
Mod4 D :ToggleCmd {ShowDesktop} {DeIconify all originquiet}
Control Mod1 L :Exec xscreensaver-command -lock

!Fluxbox
Mod4 space :Exec fbrun
Control Escape :Exec xkill
Mod4 Shift R :Restart 
Control Mod1 BackSpace :Exec exit

!Executables
Mod1 F3 :Exec gnome-terminal
F12 :Exec firefox

!Amarok
Mod4 Control Right :Exec amarok -f
Mod4 Control Left :Exec amarok -r
Mod4 Control Up :Exec amarok -p
Mod4 Control Down :Exec amarok --pause
Mod4 Control End :Exec amarok -s
